@startuml
!theme plain
title 03. Model/Object/Corpus Tiers
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Model registry" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Object store" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "RDMA hydration" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "GPU/host cache" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "RAG corpus" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : versioned weights
N2 --> N3 : adapters/tokenizers
N3 --> N4 : prefetch
N4 --> N5 : residency

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
